%N A016080 Inverse of 2071st cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A016080 Periodic with period length 2071. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A016080 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A016080/b016080.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..3000</a>
%H A016080 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 2071.
%H A016080 <a href="/index/Rec#order_1944">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 1944.
%H A016080 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A016080 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%t A016080 CoefficientList[Series[1/Cyclotomic[2071,x],{x,0,120}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Dec 24 2025 *)
%o A016080 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(2071)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
